18. Sustainable Agriculture Youth Leaders Program
SEARCA (Southeast Asian Regional Center for Graduate Study and Research in Agriculture)
ONLINE certificate program
8-week course: Jan 20 - March 14, 2026 / Self-paced with weekly live sessions (Fridays 6PM)
FREE for ASEAN youth
Partners: FAO, Asian Farmers Association
Modules: climate-smart agriculture, agroecology, farm-to-market linkages
Apply: searca.org/youth-agriculture
Contact: training@searca.org